@caption Empty Stock Comparison
The stock comparison is a tool that allows you to plot different securities,
markets and indices against each other as well as view a table based 
comparison of past performance. To get started, click the 'Add Stock', 'Add Market'
or 'Add Index' button above. Once you have added a few securities to this
comparison you can click on of the Table or Chart tabs at the top (e.g. Daily 
Chart). You can setup a new comparison with different securities by clicking 
on the 'New Comparison' button on the left.
